        "content": "<p>fitzgen opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13294\">PR #13294</a> from <code>fitzgen:more-wast-config-massaging</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Should hopefully resolve issues I'm seeing in CI like</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">failures</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">----</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">oracles</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">tests</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">wast_smoke_test</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stdout</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">----</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">thread</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"na\">oracles</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">tests</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">wast_smoke_test</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">7102</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">panicked</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">crates</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">fuzzing</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">oracles</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">777</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n<span class=\"nc\">called</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">unwrap</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">on</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">an</span